title: I'll Name This Podcast Later Episode 13
description: Episode 13 and there is something for everybody; Marisa being flown out to Philadelphia, Rory's trip to Miami, the NOME 5 rap battle, "Mari's Sports Desk", and DeflateGate to start the podcast. The latter part takes a sharp left when the question of "Have you ever pissed on somebody?" is asked; as well as the return of "I'll Respond To This Email Later" which leads to Marisa being a tad bit sensitive. *****If you want to write into the show and ask us for advice on something going on in your life, or would like to tell us a story, or just tell us how much you enjoy our amazing podcast email illnamethispodcastlater@gmail.com we will pick a few each week and read them on the show!***** SUBSCRIBE at itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/ill-n…i=335888425&mt=2 ....and rate, comment, etc!
